      • docValueCount

        public int docValueCount()
        从类复制的说明: SortedBinaryDocValues
        Retrieves the number of values for the current document. This must always be greater than zero. It is illegal to call this method after SortedBinaryDocValues.advanceExact(int) returned false.

      • nextValue

        public final org.apache.lucene.util.BytesRef nextValue()
        从类复制的说明: SortedBinaryDocValues
        Iterates to the next value in the current document. Do not call this more than SortedBinaryDocValues.docValueCount() times for the document. Note that the returned BytesRef might be reused across invocations.
